Muchidzidzo chePimanzvimbo (Geometry, [[tsazano]] (Square) chiumbwa chine mativi mana ose akaenzana negonya ina dzose dzakaenzana. Tsazano riri mumupanda wegonyaina.

==Pimamuganhu neRuvanze==

[[Pimamuganhu]] ye[[tsazano]] rine mativi akareba nhambwe '''K''' inowanikwa ne[[tsazaniso]] inoti:  

'''Pimamuganhu, P  =  4.K''',

uye [[ruvanze]] rwe[[tsazano]] runowanikwa netsazaniso inoti:

'''Ruvanze, A  =  K<sup>2</sup>'''
